static const FrontierLedgerEntry kEntries_endgame_en_trails[] = {
    { "Blood-Marked Ledger | Main Story | Completed", "Trace the ledger clues pushing John from Beecher's Hope into Blackwater's contract web. Follow courier scraps, broker notes, and the first frontier leads until the war becomes visible. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: Unlock Blackwater contract routing, Open Beecher's Hope briefing board" },
    { "Dead Courier Satchel | Main Story | Completed", "Recover the dead courier's satchel before scavengers erase the first clean clue chain. This is the first hard proof that the frontier pressure is organized: a satchel, a seal, and a route tied back to Blackwater. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: Courier proof, First broker evidence, Route mechanic sketch" },
    { "First Workbench Expansion | House Objective | Completed", "Secure salvage and leather to push Beecher's Hope from a field bench into a true workshop. This is the first real farm-upgrade-return milestone and the gate into broader crafting depth. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: Workbench Tier 2, Hub upgrade slot, Map board readiness" },
    { "Blackwater Broker | Contract | Completed", "Turn Beecher's Hope into a lawful contract lane through Blackwater intermediaries. Use the city node as a stable source of jobs, leverage, and gated workshop expansion materials. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: Contract board cadence, Trade standing, Broker-only materials" },
    { "Great Plains Salvage Lane | Contract | Completed", "Open the Great Plains convoy-salvage route that feeds the ranch and the armory. Track ambush sites, wreckage, and mixed-threat supply lanes until the region becomes a dependable loop. Region: Great Plains / Tall Trees Rewards: Consistent salvage flow, Armory parts, Route intel" },
    { "Rusk, The Collector's Dog | Elite Hunt | Completed", "Break the first named elite before Silas's outer route web hardens into a real network. Rusk is the first sign that named enemies carry real identity, route ownership, and upgrade-value drops instead of just more health. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: Named elite proof, Silas schematic clue, Boss prep momentum" },
    { "Map Intelligence Board | House Objective | Completed", "Convert loose rumors into a proper frontier map board inside Beecher's Hope. The board should track danger lanes, faction pressure, elite nests, and boss clue regions. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: Frontier Map page, Danger zone tracking, Faction route visibility" },
    { "Beecher's Hope War Room | House Objective | Completed", "Push Beecher's Hope from a workshop into a war-room with supply prep, route command, and campaign stock. This is the moment the ranch becomes a headquarters, not just a place to dump materials and leave again. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: War-room state, Support cabinet, Late-tier route command" },
    { "Silas Redd Hunt | Boss Hunt | Completed", "Build enough force, gear, and clue coverage to confront Silas Redd. This is the first named boss chain and the first major frontier escalation check. Region: Great Plains / Tall Trees Rewards: Boss trophy board unlock, World Tier 2 anchor, Named weapon parts" },
    { "Lemoyne Relic Whispers | Side Chain | Completed", "Push beyond grounded outlaw work and start the first real relic thread in Lemoyne. Recover clues, rare silver, and cult-linked notes without fully breaking Red Dead's grounded tone too early. Region: Lemoyne Rewards: Relic Hunter branch readiness, Late-game myth pipeline, Rare craft inputs" },
    { "Trophy Hall | House Objective | Completed", "Turn Beecher's Hope into a record of named kills, recovered relics, and escalating frontier war spoils. This is the point where the ranch starts feeling like a campaign hub instead of a safe house. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: Boss archive expansion, Collection wall, Late-game hub identity" },
    { "Blackwater Contract Board | Repeatable | Repeatable", "Repeat lawful contracts for broker standing, workshop supplies, and controlled XP flow. This board is the low-chaos repeatable lane for players who want steady frontier progress. Region: West Elizabeth Rewards: XP, Trade standing, Workshop materials" },
    { "Relic Recovery Routes | Repeatable | Repeatable", "Cycle dangerous relic recovery jobs once the frontier opens beyond grounded bandit work. These routes are the first scalable myth-pressure contracts and feed rare crafting paths. Region: Lemoyne Rewards: Relic materials, Boss clue fragments, Collection progress" },
};
